data.description: Welcome to this one of a kind, renovated ranch home in Warminster Township! Be welcomed by a beautiful open floor plan that features a spacious living room complimented by a bay window bringing in beautiful natural light. The newly finished kitchen has stainless steel appliances, gas cooking, beautifully finished granite countertops and ample cabinet space. Additionally, the island serves as eat-in seating. The laundry room adjoins the kitchen creating easy, one floor living without the hassle of steps. In addition to a formal living area, there is a more private entertainment room for movie nights or office space. The back patio doors join in at the kitchen creating easy access to the back deck which overlooks a generously sized, fenced backyard awaiting your personal upgrades. This home has three bedrooms which share a hall bathroom. This home is nestled into a quiet neighborhood in the Spring Lake Farms development in Centennial School District. Schedule your showing today.
